data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home nestled within the charming Sherborne Manor neighborhood. This home offers a blend of space and flexibility tailored perfectly for growing families. The first floor showcases an open floor plan with a versatile bedroom and an en-suite bathroom which provides an ideal retreat for in-laws or guests, while also serving as a convenient office or flex room. The chef's kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, stainless steel appliances and expansive granite countertops which seamlessly connect to the family room with a cozy gas fireplace- great for family gatherings. Upstairs, the primary suite exudes luxury with a spa-like bathroom and dual walk-in closets.  Three additional bedrooms offer comfort and privacy, accompanied by a hall bathroom. A vast loft area presents endless possibilities, whether utilized as a second living space or a dynamic play area for the entire family to enjoy. This one won't last long, schedule your showing today!
